title: Fighting for Honor, Okanogan Valley Pride, Book 1
description: There's only one rightful Alpha, and he's back to claim his pride and his mate…As the rightful Alpha of a unique pride of panthers, originally founded by his father, Dominic Stone followed his inherent solitary path to find peace and grieve the untimely demise of his sire. Five years later, he returns home ready to take his place, settle old debts and claim the one woman he’s always wanted as his.
author: Kacey Hammell
